{"tid":1145144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★圓方招牌起火冒煙！","createTime":"2019-05-08T13:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T06:19:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d3dd601619428bdf0323686553d2672aad85bcfc","tid":1145144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190508/photo/bkn-20190508191338769-0508_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190508211223\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190508%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190508191338769-0508_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190508211223&h=c9012d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀柯士甸道西1號、港鐵九龍站圓方商場，今日(8日)傍晚6時許，上址一塊面向佐敦道與雅翔道交界行車天橋的大型外牆標誌燈牌，突然冒煙起火，多名駕駛人士途經見狀，紛紛報警求助。消防員接報趕至，開動一條喉灌救，約10分鐘後將火救熄，事件中無人受傷及毋須疏散。圓方發言人表示，商場運作不受影響，正調查起火原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190508/bkn-20190508191338769-0508_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190508%2Fbkn-20190508191338769-0508_00822_001.html&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=2eaa4f46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190508/bkn-20190508191338769-0508_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ccabff4b1d196f1aea40736de8b2fa16cf52d07","tid":1145144,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9a64796ef3be78fad2241f793407f906c0d77e","tid":1145144,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"火燒圓方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6fc0e18410ceb186c0b5c66ff53f6efcadf08f2","tid":1145144,"uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"4c9a64796ef3be78fad2241f793407f906c0d77e","tid":1145144,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"